testCopyAtomAndBondAttributesById

public void testCopyAtomAndBondAttributesById()
copies attributes on bonds and atoms to another molecule. for each atom/bond in this.molecule finds Id and hence corresponding atom/bond in 'to'. Copies all attributes from that atom to to.atom/@* If corresponding atom does not exist, throws exception. If target attribute exists throws exception

Parameters:
to -
Throws:
CMLRuntimeException - ids in molecules do not correspond or attributes are already present
